Package: colloid-icon-theme
Architecture: all
Section: misc
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Colorful, modern icon theme for linux desktops
 The icon-theme is complemented by the colloid-gtk-theme

Package: colloid-cursors
Architecture: all
Section: misc
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Stylish and colorful colloid based cursors
 The cursor-theme is complemented by the colloid-gtk-theme
 .
 This package will install the Colloid cursor theme to Colloid-cursors
 and the Colloid-dark cursor theme to Colloid-white-cursors for clarificaton
 and consistency with other themes from the same author
